The roster shall also contain the social security number, name, and permanent address of each eligible student enrolled at the institution, his or her enrollment status, the amount of tuition specific aid (grant money, scholarship, tuition or fee
        waivers, or tuition remission) the student received, the amount of tuition and fees charged the student for the payment period, the amount of tuition and fees that would be charged to an in-State student (if a public institution) for that payment
        period; the award amount that should be paid to the institution on behalf of the student for that payment period;
